### Get Matches List
GET http://localhost:8000/matches


###
POST http://localhost:8000/matches
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sport": "football",
    "homeTeam": "Man United",
    "awayTeam": "Man City",
    "startTime": "2026-07-15T01:43:00+00:00",
    "endTime": "2026-07-15T03:43:00+00:00"
}

### Create Match
POST http://localhost:8000/matches
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sport": "football",
    "homeTeam": "LFC",
    "awayTeam": "MCFC",
    "startTime": "2026-07-15T01:45:00+00:00",
    "endTime": "2026-07-15T03:43:00+00:00"
}